{"type": "article", "id": 4778, "title": "Mavari 多功能性防水披风", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-29T07:21:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233621QwDLzp1MbuNUSd2W.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tMavari 是一个实用的多功能性防水披风，由 Juan Carlos Viso 、 Bryan Capriles 与 Oscar Solorzano 三位设计师推出。设计团队选用了高质的面料织物，使其拥有保温、隔热、防水、放风等多种功能，是户外休闲的合适伴侣。如果下雨的话，你只需要把它往身上一披，就能抵挡雨水侵袭，此外，它还拥有快干特性，亦能够作为毛巾实用。当然，景观简单几个步骤，这件防水披风还可以快速变为一个背包，没地方收纳的话，直接背起来就好啦。目前，Mavari 正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，售价 145 美元（约合人民币 903 元）起，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/mavaricode/m-a-v-a-r-i\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"http://www.designboom.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/designboom-818.gif\" width=\"640\" alt=\"\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052336198sDUmqKF5hgIcVEY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6765625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233619QTIvk0KwOX4LR39u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5609375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233619QLAVFJI7ze3rWy61.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7203125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233620EQHKjfI54zqRAyMg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7203125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233620BWLD5S8fYpktcmGx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7203125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}